text:
(1)
Astoria Park, showing a small cottage opposite 24th Road in the Park. The Mallison Silk Mills at the left, face Twenty-fourth Ave.

April 1925.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2)
The same, from another angle showing also the Hell Gate Bridge in the background.

March 14, 1931.

P. L. Sperr.
title: Queens: Astoria Park.
